law.catch_line: Execution not to issue for ten days -- Exception.
law.text: No execution shall issue on any judgment, unless ordered by the court, until after the expiration of ten days from the rendition thereof.
law.history: Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1653.
